      <title>工党誓言成立英国足球监管机构；关注转会税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/labour-vows-to-set-up-uk-football-regulator-eyes-transfer-levy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党承诺成立一个新的足球监管机构，并表示如果赢得下个月的大选，该机构可能会监管门票销售并审查对英超足球俱乐部征收转会税的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/labour-vows-to-set-up-uk-football-regulator-eyes-transfer-levy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 18:37:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
